	<description><![CDATA[<img src="/media/templates/site/atomic/images/template_preview.png" alt="Atomic Template Preview" style="max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin-bottom:1rem;border:1px solid #ccc"><p>Atomic is an easy-to-modify and minimal example of a Joomla template using Bootstrap. It was previously included in Joomla 2.5.</p><p><a href="https://atomic.kontentdesign.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Demo Site</a> &nbsp;|&nbsp; <a href="https://github.com/Kontent/Atomic" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub Repository</a></p>]]></description>
